Class FIdentifiables<V>

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CIdentifieds, FSlots

    public abstract class FIdentifiables<V>
extends uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon_util.KKeyedList<java.lang.String,V>
    Abstract class whose extensions represent ordered lists, with element value-types that enable each value to be mapped to an associated CIdentity object, where that identity object can be retrieved via the value object itself.

    The "keys" for the version of KKeyedList that this class extends will be the "identifier" values from the identities to which the values are mapped (see CIdentity.getIdentifier()).

    See ancestor classes for details of additional list-operations and associated listening mechanisms.
